## Architecture

Monorepo with MVVM across all platforms. API-first: OpenAPI spec drives typed clients.

```
{% if "backend" in platforms %}backend/       → Spring Boot 4 (Kotlin 2.2+, Java 21) — Azure Container Apps{% endif %}
{% if "web" in platforms %}web/           → Next.js + TypeScript — Cloudflare Pages{% endif %}
{% if "admin" in platforms %}admin/         → Next.js + TypeScript (admin portal) — Cloudflare Pages{% endif %}
{% if "android" in platforms %}android/       → Kotlin + Jetpack Compose (MVVM, Hilt, Room){% endif %}
{% if "ios" in platforms %}ios/           → Swift 6 + SwiftUI (MVVM, SwiftData) — Mac/Xcode only{% endif %}
shared/        → OpenAPI spec + design tokens
docs/          → Living documentation (entities, features, deployment)
```

