## Key Documentation

- `docs/architecture.md` — system design, platform map, tech decisions
- `docs/entities/` — entity definitions, fields, relationships
- `docs/features/` — feature specs with business logic and board review
- `docs/api/conventions.md` — API naming, pagination, error format
- `docs/advisory-board.md` — virtual advisory board personas
- `docs/deployment/` — Azure, Cloudflare, CI/CD setup
- `shared/api-contracts/openapi.yml` — API contract (source of truth)

## Conventions

- **API-first**: Define endpoints in OpenAPI → generate clients → implement
- **MVVM**: ViewModel + UiState/ViewState on both Android and iOS
- **DI**: Hilt (Android), protocol-based container (iOS), Spring (backend)
- **Tests**: MockK + Turbine (Android), XCTest (iOS), JUnit Jupiter 6 (backend)
- **Feature docs include Board Review** from virtual advisory board
- **One ViewModel per screen**, repositories are protocol/interface + impl

